<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Data_remanence&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: Software">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Software</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Darik%27s_Boot_and_Nuke" title="Darik's Boot and Nuke">Darik's Boot and Nuke</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Shred_(Unix)" title="Shred (Unix)">shred</a> (part of the <a href="/wiki/GNU" title="GNU">GNU</a> <a href="/wiki/Coreutils" title="Coreutils" class="mw-redirect">Coreutils</a> package)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Blancco" title="Blancco">Blancco</a></li>
<li>PGP Desktop</li>
<li>SDelete is <a href="/wiki/Data_erasure#Standards" title="Data erasure">standards</a> compliant<sup id="cite_ref-12" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-12" title=""><span>[</span>13<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
</ul>
<p>There are dozens of other tools for various operating systems.</p>
