<li id="cite_note-skorobogatov-6"><b><a href="#cite_ref-skorobogatov_6-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFSergei_Skorobogatov2002">Sergei Skorobogatov (June 2002). <i><a href="http://www.cl.cam.ac.uk/techreports/UCAM-CL-TR-536.html" class="external text" title="http://www.cl.cam.ac.uk/techreports/UCAM-CL-TR-536.html" rel="nofollow">Low temperature data remanence in static RAM</a></i>. University of Cambridge, Computer Laboratory<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.cl.cam.ac.uk/techreports/UCAM-CL-TR-536.html" class="external free" title="http://www.cl.cam.ac.uk/techreports/UCAM-CL-TR-536.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.cl.cam.ac.uk/techreports/UCAM-CL-TR-536.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Low+temperature+data+remanence+in+static+RAM&amp;rft.aulast=Sergei+Skorobogatov&amp;rft.au=Sergei+Skorobogatov&amp;rft.date=June+2002&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Cambridge%2C+Computer+Laboratory&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cl.cam.ac.uk%2Ftechreports%2FUCAM-CL-TR-536.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Data_remanence"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Halderman-7">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Halderman_7-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Halderman_7-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFJ._Alex_Halderman.2C_et_al.2008">J. Alex Halderman, et al. (February 2008) (PDF). <i><a href="http://citp.princeton.edu.nyud.net/pub/coldboot.pdf" class="external text" title="http://citp.princeton.edu.nyud.net/pub/coldboot.pdf" rel="nofollow">Lest We Remember: Cold Boot Attacks on Encryption Keys</a></i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://citp.princeton.edu.nyud.net/pub/coldboot.pdf" class="external free" title="http://citp.princeton.edu.nyud.net/pub/coldboot.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://citp.princeton.edu.nyud.net/pub/coldboot.pdf</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Lest+We+Remember%3A+Cold+Boot+Attacks+on+Encryption+Keys&amp;rft.aulast=J.+Alex+Halderman%2C+et+al.&amp;rft.au=J.+Alex+Halderman%2C+et+al.&amp;rft.date=February+2008&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcitp.princeton.edu.nyud.net%2Fpub%2Fcoldboot.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Data_remanence"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-NISPOM-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-NISPOM_8-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="https://www.dss.mil/portal/ShowBinary/BEA%20Repository/new_dss_internet/isp/fac_clear/download_nispom.html" class="external text" title="https://www.dss.mil/portal/ShowBinary/BEA%20Repository/new_dss_internet/isp/fac_clear/download_nispom.html" rel="nofollow">"Download NISPOM"</a>. <a href="/wiki/Defense_Security_Service" title="Defense Security Service">DSS</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="https://www.dss.mil/portal/ShowBinary/BEA%20Repository/new_dss_internet/isp/fac_clear/download_nispom.html" class="external free" title="https://www.dss.mil/portal/ShowBinary/BEA%20Repository/new_dss_internet/isp/fac_clear/download_nispom.html" rel="nofollow">https://www.dss.mil/portal/ShowBinary/BEA%20Repository/new_dss_internet/isp/fac_clear/download_nispom.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-11-25</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Download+NISPOM&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BDefense+Security+Service%7CDSS%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dss.mil%2Fportal%2FShowBinary%2FBEA%2520Repository%2Fnew_dss_internet%2Fisp%2Ffac_clear%2Fdownload_nispom.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Data_remanence"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
